# 13_density_and_measure_popovers — substrate-layer suite for the
# density and measure-tool popovers (s195 m6).
#
# Substrate-style test (per TESTING.md grandfather clause): each
# sub-test proves the substrate contract holds — abbrev resolves,
# verbs dispatch, queries read back. Baselines are hardcoded
# explicitly rather than captured (the DSL doesn't have variable
# capture yet — banked as a gap).
#
# The tested abbrevs:
#
#   Density popover  pop_tb_dn_com  (Comfortable — launch default)
#                    pop_tb_dn_std  (Standard)
#                    pop_tb_dn_cpt  (Compact)
#                    pop_tb_dn_tgt  (Tight)
#
#   Measure popover  pop_tb_meas_sv (save measurements)
#                    pop_tb_meas_dc (delete on copy)
#
# Side effects: the script flips through density modes and ends on
# Comfortable (the launch default). If you had density set to
# something else, this test will reset it — explicit hardcoded
# baseline per TESTING.md's grandfather discipline. Measure-popover
# settings are restored to false at the end (their launch default).
#
# Test protocol:
#   1. Open the Scripter window.
#   2. Load this script.
#   3. Run. Every line should PASS.

#[sub] Density radio — labels read back from the registry.

assert pop_tb_dn_com label == "Comfortable"
assert pop_tb_dn_std label == "Standard"
assert pop_tb_dn_cpt label == "Compact"
assert pop_tb_dn_tgt label == "Tight"

#[sub] Density radio — Comfortable wins.

pop_tb_dn_com set true
assert pop_tb_dn_com active == true
assert pop_tb_dn_std active == false
assert pop_tb_dn_cpt active == false
assert pop_tb_dn_tgt active == false

#[sub] Density radio — Standard wins.

pop_tb_dn_std set true
assert pop_tb_dn_std active == true
assert pop_tb_dn_com active == false
assert pop_tb_dn_cpt active == false
assert pop_tb_dn_tgt active == false

#[sub] Density radio — Compact wins.

pop_tb_dn_cpt set true
assert pop_tb_dn_cpt active == true
assert pop_tb_dn_com active == false
assert pop_tb_dn_std active == false
assert pop_tb_dn_tgt active == false

#[sub] Density radio — Tight wins.

pop_tb_dn_tgt set true
assert pop_tb_dn_tgt active == true
assert pop_tb_dn_com active == false
assert pop_tb_dn_std active == false
assert pop_tb_dn_cpt active == false

#[sub] Density — restore to Comfortable (launch default).

pop_tb_dn_com set true
assert pop_tb_dn_com active == true

#[sub] Measure popover — save toggle round-trip.

pop_tb_meas_sv set true
assert pop_tb_meas_sv active == true
pop_tb_meas_sv set false
assert pop_tb_meas_sv active == false

#[sub] Measure popover — delete-on-copy toggle round-trip.

pop_tb_meas_dc set true
assert pop_tb_meas_dc active == true
pop_tb_meas_dc set false
assert pop_tb_meas_dc active == false

#[sub] Done. 6 new substrate widgets, all addressable.
